T*
(- How would you avoid the mistake described as assuming AI always understands) Tj
T*
(information like a person?) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Study Tips After Reading) Tj
T*
(- Rewrite the overview of AI in your own words after studying it.) Tj
T*
(- Use short exercises built around AI concept and ethics questions before trying harder) Tj
T*
(tasks.) Tj
T*
(- Keep track of mistakes such as assuming AI always understands information like a) Tj
T*
(person and write the correction beside each one.) Tj
T*
(- Revise AI regularly so the method behind pattern recognition, learning from data, and) Tj
T*
(responsible use becomes familiar.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Independent Practice) Tj
T*
(- Explain the overview of AI and describe how it fits into Computer Science.) Tj
T*
(- Work through an example based on describing how a recommendation system works and) Tj
T*
(explain each step.) Tj
T*
(- Describe why assuming AI always understands information like a person causes errors) Tj
T*
(and how to avoid it.) Tj
